The source code for Revitar 2 should be available in the same place as the built package.

This package is built with (or is configured to be built with) statically linked libraries from glibc and libstdc++.
glibc is available here: http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/glibc/
It is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License version 2.1, available here: http://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Copying.html
libstdc++ is available here: http://gcc.gnu.org/libstdc++/
It is licensed under a modified version of the GNU General Public License version 3, available here: http://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/libstdc++/manual/license.html

This package was built using the VST SDK 2.4.2, avaliable here: http://www.steinberg.net/en/company/developer.html
VST Plugin Interface Technology is by Steinberg Soft- und Hardware GmbH.

